"msg":"更新返件事先 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/01/P2017020100443.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201702%2F01%2FP2017020100443.htm&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a1b76465\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201702/01/P2017020100443.htm</a> <br />\n警方呼籲市民提供屯門失蹤女子消息（附圖） <br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊ <br />\n　　警方今日（二月一日）呼籲市民提供一名在屯門失蹤女子的消息。 <br />\n<br />\n　　七十歲女子樂翠娟一月二十六日上午離開其位於屯門龍門路的住所後便告失蹤，其家人翌日向警方報案。 <br />\n<br />\n　　她身高約一點五五米，體重約五十公斤，中等身材，圓面型，黃皮膚及蓄短直黑髮。<span style=\"color: red;\">她最後露面時身穿黑色上衣、黑色外套、黑色褲、拖鞋及戴眼鏡</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n　　任何人如有該失蹤女子的消息或曾見過她，請致電三六六一　三一一二或六二七三　五七八七，或電郵至rmpu-ntn-1@police.gov.hk與新界北總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。 <br />\n<br />\n完 <br />\n2017年2月1日（星期三） <br />\n香港時間14時10分"},{"pid":"c0ba73499cf85016d4b7ed1337625f8b412be077","tid":103141,"uid":57867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53403549d0d1301ae001ea65cced413df400d10e","tid":103141,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18767cac67560a35a64dba388918056b6b862651","tid":103141,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b361351fefdf82023924ace7a7dfa1817f3106","tid":103141,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b00839c83df88346121a3938ee5602613d2a71aa","tid":103141,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef0686ee37a0bc182f1a68f8bbc65bba0bbe8a63","tid":103141,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800dbf7cc0ebc1082e395e1cd86e5e3da9ae13f7","tid":103141,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"